# React Components

- Default to **server components**; add `'use client'` only for `useState`, `useEffect`, event handlers, or browser APIs
- Styling via Tailwind utility classes only
- Reusable primitives go in `components/ui/`; dashboard UI in `components/dashboard/`

## Marketing UI (FlowShift design system)

- Dark shell: `bg-zinc-950`, borders `border-zinc-800`, primary actions `bg-sky-600`
- `MarketingPage` — public layout with header + footer; use `variant="auth"` for login/signup
- `MarketingCard`, `MarketingButton`, `SectionHeader`, `CheckList` in `components/marketing/primitives.tsx`
- Auth forms use `AuthPageShell` + shared `authLinkClass` / `authButtonClass`

## Dashboard

- `(dashboard)/layout.tsx` — sidebar shell; auth guard via middleware
- Protected routes: `/dashboard`, `/clients`, `/log`, `/reports`, `/settings`
- Show loading states and explicit error messages — never silent failures
- Use `Badge` for activity types and status chips
- Currency via `formatMoney()` from `@/lib/reports`

## Forms

- `ActivityLogForm` — manual entry + optional expense/deal + voice memo upload
- `NewClientForm` — creates client via `/api/clients`
- Validate on server with zod; surface API errors in red helper text
